snippet.title: PlayStation - Subete ga F Ninaru - The Perfect Insider (2002)
snippet.description:
DESCRIPTION
Subete ga F Ninaru: The Perfect Insider is an Adventure game, developed by Kid and published by Electronic Arts Victor, which was released in Japan in 2002.
